Below is a **complete end-to-end Ansible role implementation** for **MicroStrategy Environment deployment on OpenShift**, including everything you requested:

✔ Login with **FID/password**
✔ Validate **SMCP health**
✔ Validate **SMMR status**
✔ Create **Namespace**
✔ Add namespace to **ServiceMeshMemberRoll**
✔ Deploy **MicroStrategy Environment (CR YAML)**
