# 5️⃣ Login to OpenShift

`tasks/login.yml`

```yaml
- name: Login to OpenShift
  shell: >
    oc login {{ ocp_api }}
    -u {{ ocp_user }}
    -p {{ ocp_password }}
    --insecure-skip-tls-verify
  register: login_output
```

---

# 6️⃣ Validate SMCP

`tasks/validate_smcp.yml`

```yaml
- name: Check SMCP status
  shell: >
    oc get smcp -n istio-system
    -o jsonpath='{.items[0].status.conditions[?(@.type=="Ready")].status}'
  register: smcp_status

- name: Fail if SMCP not ready
  fail:
    msg: "ServiceMeshControlPlane is not ready"
  when: smcp_status.stdout != "True"
```

---

# 7️⃣ Validate SMMR

`tasks/validate_smmr.yml`

```yaml
- name: Validate SMMR configuration
  shell: >
    oc get smmr default -n istio-system
    -o jsonpath='{.status.configuredMembers}'
  register: smmr_status
```

