# 8️⃣ Create Namespace

`tasks/namespace.yml`

```yaml
- name: Create namespace
  kubernetes.core.k8s:
    state: present
    definition:
      apiVersion: v1
      kind: Namespace
      metadata:
        name: "{{ namespace }}"
```

---

# 9️⃣ Add namespace to Service Mesh

`tasks/smmr.yml`

```yaml
- name: Get existing SMMR
  kubernetes.core.k8s_info:
    api_version: maistra.io/v1
    kind: ServiceMeshMemberRoll
    name: default
    namespace: istio-system
  register: smmr

- name: Update ServiceMeshMemberRoll
  kubernetes.core.k8s:
    state: present
    definition:
      apiVersion: maistra.io/v1
      kind: ServiceMeshMemberRoll
      metadata:
        name: default
        namespace: istio-system
      spec:
        members: "{{ smmr.resources[0].spec.members + [namespace] | unique }}"
```

